Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:02.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I tried approaching slowly,\Nbut it ran away when I got right near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.70,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I really need to give her an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.57,sign_10275_162_The_Answer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,550)}The Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Furuya-kun, I've waited long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can talk about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.75,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Your username.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you have an answer for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if you're serious\Nor just playing me, Minagawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll ask seriously this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So that's a no, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you aren't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that I'm not interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't bring myself to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:50.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if you're serious\Nor playing me {\i1}either{\i0}, Furuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.54,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she would give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.45,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.83,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What if she's acting,\Nand she's waiting for me to stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.52,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:10.80,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.63,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I made her wait so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.62,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try talking to her again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.01,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She must be feeling at least some remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.95,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.28,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't given up, she's lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.62,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame her. I'm so indecisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.48,sign_12156_194_Minagawa_Yuki__W,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Minagawa Yuki {\b0}\NWhy are you staring at me? \N(¬_¬)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.91,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How could she tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.95,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I thought she was angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.20,sign_12323_197_Why_are_you_star,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me? \N(¬_¬)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.20,sign_12323_198_I_m_not_trying_t,->,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.20,sign_12363_199_Huh___You_were_a,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You were actually staring??\NLOL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:39.80,Italics,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.82,Italics,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like teasing you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.54,Italics,<-,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any hurry for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.15,Italics,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.04,sign_12637_205_Actually___never,<-,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, \Nnever mind lol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.04,Default,<-,0000,0000,0000,,"Actually, never mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:56.86,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!\NHe was actually staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:03.48,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,My friend handed me a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.03,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To be delivered to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:13.36,sign_13161_211_You_re_Beautiful,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}You're Beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sorry to do this during exams,\Nbut we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Do you have time after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I totally do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Anything for you, Takano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.83,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He really is a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:22.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A letter? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected this from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's from Yoshinaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And she wanted me to ask you for your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is more stressful\Nfor you than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice, Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell Yoshinaga I said sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:56.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but she didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That actually happens, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to try again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, apparently, I'm just a nice guy to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She and I sound similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do\Nif I confessed to you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have any fun dating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think my crush would say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She sounds like a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should be a bit proactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Try hugging her, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like in dramas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,where the guy hugs the girl\Nand shouts that he loves her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wouldn't it bother you\Nif someone did that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:45.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a nice person,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,so I might be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Does that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We need to study for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've decided to give up on confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:25.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not end up getting friend-zoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't know what to do\Nif I confessed to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not the person you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You said it would bother you,\Nso it's probably hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Should I not have said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,About my answer to Yoshinaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn her down myself tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:52.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She had to go through you, but she had the\Ncourage to confess, and I want to honor that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck on exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:09.55,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's so kind.\NHe's such a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.66,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.22,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:24.58,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not that that would ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Watching You From Afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.97,Next_Ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Watching You From Afar
